metadata.name: All the Bandwidth You Need 1/1
metadata.description:
Concealed behind an underground handbook for the electronic frontier. True nyms of digital signatures. Wide eyed creators dreaming of ideas and code.  Reflective black bug eyes shades, checkered denim and cotton sleeve jacket, printed cypherdelic tee, ripped cutout slim fit jeans. 

Synth Graph: a center front view 2012 portrait of a beautiful female wearing high fashion streetwear, blue ripped jeans, patchwork oversized sweatshirt, white cateye sunglasses, a red bandana tying back her hair, underground crowded rune pub at night in the background, highly detailed, dark background, dark alley at night, grunge aesthetic. Sampler: plms, steps: 70, scale: 13.
